Welcome, mo!
For the remote Liberalitas, Yutayuta has
brought accessories, mo!

rows.label: tlk42450261_01_msg0002

Yutayuta will not forgive any frumpiness, mo!

rows.label: tlk42450261_01_msg0003

You've made a good purchase, mo!
That should get rid of the frumpiness, mo!

rows.label: tlk42450261_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Arararararararara, mo!
Do you prefer being frumpy, mo?
